Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,169.5)\c&H52D8D8&\bord1.5\3c&H65434C&\frz14}山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(835.5,151.5)\c&H52D8D8&\bord1.5\3c&H65434C&\frz9}站
