Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}什麽?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}請冷靜地聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我收到寫給玲央粉絲信的回信了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\alpha&H127\c&HE7DAFB&\bord1.5\1a&H54&\pos(1772.499,441.5)}m 0 0 l 0 0 l 225 0 l 225 420 l 0 420 l 0 0{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這不是很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我是不會對別人的粉絲回應有反應的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}沒問題 我沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就算舞菜對我多沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我也喜歡舞菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}繪里飄...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}基 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不能覺得她很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}繪里飄就是這樣保持住自我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}下次演唱會 我會把你的手燈全弄斷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我從來沒收過空音的回信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你什麼時候寄出的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}說不定是還沒去事務所拿 還沒收到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}話說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我沒寫信給舞菜過耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不會吧! ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}反正又不會有回信 握手會也能見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你在握手會都沒握到手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你的牙齒也要全部弄斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有沒有喜歡上粉絲過?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}哎 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}怎麽可能不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那種事 就像是背叛粉絲們一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可是只有繪里飄小姐只推我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}初 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}沒 我看都沒人排隊很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}其實我是推真妃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不說也沒差吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我沒勇氣去見空音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這什麼意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be30}空音 好開心你能記得我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}總是和繪里飄小姐一起 推玲央的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}謝謝你 我們第一次見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是要改成推我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過 説不定是和繪里飄小姐閙僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的朋友是推你 可是她這次得流感不能來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}以後也請你多照顧她囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}當然 這是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}小哥你也要好好珍惜玲央喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}小文你覺得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我從來沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這對小孩還太早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我又不是小孩!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}抱歉 我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}優佳傳 Line 說她快到了 後面麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你們感情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}才沒有好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那 明天見囉?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}打工加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你們也加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}小文真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}一直在裝優佳的白色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}現...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}現在那傢伙絕對在這!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}糟糕糟糕 跑到冰箱那裡了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}早...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}咦? 我還以為是優佳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我剛好到附近就來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}話說優佳傳 Line 說家裡有蟑螂會遲到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}為什麼是傳給你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不知道 傳錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我昨天晚上和優佳在傳 Line 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那傢伙完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}粉絲信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我也要帶回家 才不會堆著沒回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真好 我從來沒收到粉絲信過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}呃 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}繪里飄小姐也沒寫?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我也好想寫回信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要是見面會很緊張 如果是寫信一定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\alpha&H127\bord1.5\1a&H54&\pos(156.5,187.5)}m 0 0 l 0 0 l 300 0 l 300 180 l 0 180 l 0 0{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}一定能率直地寫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在握手會的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}麻煩她寫信給你如何呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯...可是要自己說...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那麽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1050)}{\be30}我在下次演唱會 MC 時會問現在想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs36\pos(886.5,960)\be30}曲間問候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你就說想要粉絲寫的信吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這點小事可以吧 玲央
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}金金...金龜...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}糟糕糟糕糟糕 為啥要來我家! ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這是非法入侵啊! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}小夢 女生狂歡節 你有在觀眾席吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}討厭 我去是不想被你發現的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不管你在哪裡 我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我沒騙過你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}明年要一起上場喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是優佳傳的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真是的...
